s wrong.  Yes this is only a game.  Yes this is for fun. Yes I play evil characters, and they do some pretty abhorent things, but they do not do things that hurt the fun of the people controlling the characters behind this game, and the inconsiderate and immature actions of which Xott is speaking do cause that type of harm.  All that being said there is no way to get through the low-brow, idiocy, nor the uncontrollable immaturity that makes up the web and this game.  As long as these sites and games house the undisciplined and unsupervised children (mentally and physically age challenged) of the world, we will continue to see this &quot;diverity&quot; of belief structure and behavior.  Now please flame on, and please use your best and basest language to prove my point.
